===[[Season 1]]===
Ser Aron is present at a court session in the [[Red Keep]] in which [[Janos Slynt]] is created [[House Slynt|Lord Slynt]] and given the castle of [[Harrenhal]] and later [[Knight|Ser]] [[Barristan Selmy]] is dismissed from the [[Kingsguard]]. When [[Sansa Stark]] appears to ask for mercy for her [[Eddard Stark|father]], she greets Ser Aron, though the knight turns away.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Pointy End]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

Ser Aron dies during the riots in King's Landing.
